 Cream Cheese Pasta Photo Little Sunny Kitchen Pasta is arguably Lagos’ staple food and ordering pasta every time you’re out has become a thing for many people. Whether cheese based or tomato based, another thing we can agree on is that Lagos restaurants price pasta as highly as they can, coupled with fine-tuned names, dark lightning and aesthetic spaces. So, save yourself some coin by learning how to make different pasta recipes right in your kitchen. Follow this detailed recipe to learn to cook cream cheese pasta: Ingredients Method